values: Don't forget to include where you heard of this journal from in your comment. Thanks.

Protagonists and Allies:
Amanda is a twenty-five year old system administrator and investigator for ASR. Her tropes, using the ones from this site, are gadgeteer genius with a bit of heroic bystander when the chips are down. She's actually a very minor character despite being the one picked to play in
polychromatic
.

Lucian was a thirty-three year old field agent for ASR, and died during an investigation. His tropes were part-time hero and bunny ears lawyer. His issues went overlooked both because of his heroic tendencies, and that the issues were harmless and didn't create to much of a setback.

Robert Mathews was a fifty-two year old military colonel, and died of complications of a heart attack. His tropes were reasonable authority figure- the reasonableness was what cost him the rank of general, actually-  and the quiet one.

Alexis was a twenty-eight year old field medic for ASR, and died due to being struck by a stray round while tending a patient during a battle. Her tropes were cool big sis and a tomato in the mirror- an unknowing clone of a doctor with the same name who died in a car accident who took the woman's place; she never discovered that.

Charles is a thirty-four year old scientist who did freelance work when research grants weren't panning out. His tropes are aloof big brother and the professor- though he does snap and become a mad scientist after a certain series of events despite not becoming evil just insane.

Villains:
Madison was a twenty-nine year old former field agent who went insane gradually during the first third of the story before defecting and becoming one of the main antagonists of the second third of the story; pre-insanity, he was almost a completely different person, though always slightly unstable. Eventually, he is killed by Lucian, but the hero dies later in the investigation from wounds obtained during the fight. His tropes were knight templar and a twisted example of the warrior poet.

[Full sketches will come later]

Public Service Announcement:
Black jelly beans taste like DEATH, please exercise caution when buying jelly beans to avoid this particular flavor. Your tastebuds, and comrades will thank you. That is all.

The boxes in the pc are getting awfully full, so I'm having a huge giveaway. All pokemon in this entry are free to a good home, and you're welcome to as many as you would like.

Dear 6A,

Due to the rampant nutcassery of both you and LJ -which is showing little sign of abating I might add-, I will be keeping a back up copy of all my entries on both my local disk, and privately on an undisclosed site. Banning or suspending me is futile, so I'm posting this notice so those concerned will be able to see it. Frankly, I don't believe I'll be violating the TOS in anyway, unless of course having a private copy of anything I post here so that I will still have my work in the event of server failure is against the TOS.

I make no profit off anything posted on this site, I will not be using lj for teh p0rnz, I will not be using LJ for file sharing or any sort of copyright infringement. Any and all content posted by me is for my own personal enjoyment, and can be viewed by whoever I add as a friend or any community that I join which deals with the subject matter.

In other words, this corner of the sandbox is not related to the fuckery your are searching for, 6A.


Not remotely love,
Acadia

PS. I hope you enjoy the font and the sparkles, 6A.
PPS. I apologize to everyone aside from 6A and LJ for any eye bleeding this proclamation caused.
